youtube-download-url
====================

Provides the Download URL for downloading youtube videos directly 


How it works:
=============

Open and Erlang shell, compile and run 
Copy the URL and paste it your browser to download the video 


ERL$> c(youtube).
{ok,youtube}
ERL$> youtube:download("http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QzfDABqVs4").
